{"tid":862322,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[跪地JJ插沙求解答]有冇大腸癌病人用緊免疫療法?","createTime":"2018-10-14T18:01:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-05T13:38:35.000Z","uid":84734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5fda6e8b442ab8b6563893ed5052e9fa377c8f89","tid":862322,"uid":84734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:01:50.000Z","msg":"我爸爸患左大腸癌四年<br />\n中間斷斷續續做左好多次化療同 標靶藥<br />\n個醫生話香港用係大腸癌嘅藥已經用過哂，但係都無作用<br />\n<br />\n而家癌症擴散到肝，個醫生仲話肝擴散得好快，半年可能就會擴散到成個肝<br />\n<br />\n因為之前嘅化療副作用太勁（甩頭髮，手腳麻痹，生暗瘡，傷口復合得好慢，肚瀉，有一次仲嚴重到屙到脫水住左幾日醫院），我爸爸拒絕左繼續做化療，轉左去睇中醫同做氣功<br />\n<br />\n轉左中醫之後，佢嘅面色的確好左好多，個人又肥返，心情又比以前好左好多，就咁睇外表係睇唔出有病<br />\n<br />\n但係西醫之前同我講得返半年時間我一直都忘記唔到，而且肝一病發，出事前本人唔會feel到有唔舒服，我呢排發夢成日都夢見佢個肝突然發病，好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最近睇到諾貝爾獎個免疫療法可以激活到自身免疫力，又冇咩副作用，睇過網上d資料講話係用係所有癌症都得，但係就偏偏搵唔到用係大腸癌嘅資料<br />\n<br />\n好想知香港有冇人做緊相關治療?<br />\n點先可以用到呢隻藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73cc445a019d2eb1333194db646eb0b5ce8b95ee","tid":862322,"uid":75232,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:15:16.000Z","msg":"你Daddy個colon cancer有無KRAS G12C mutation?<br />\n<br />\n有嘅話ARS-1620呢隻標靶藥應該work架喎...<br />\n<br />\n利申:喺美帝頭五大醫學院入面研究cancer, 包括colon cancer."},{"pid":"974ee97b744eab3b3f3a996b712a5efd15c133c7","tid":862322,"uid":43000,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:34:04.000Z","msg":"佐敦協成行7樓 施醫生有做，一針4萬幾蚊(唔同劑量唔同價錢)<br />\n我屋企人前排有cancer做左半年，好好彩癌細胞指數落返正常水平<br />\n不過唔係個個啱用同埋每次做完記得睇返癌細胞指數有無好轉，因為聽講有啲醫生好hea收完錢就算完全唔理有無成效<br />\n希望你屋企人無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3298ad8e882ebfae93279dca78b6e241f4827559","tid":862322,"uid":84734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73cc445a019d2eb1333194db646eb0b5ce8b95ee","tid":862322,"uid":75232,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:15:16.000Z","msg":"你Daddy個colon cancer有無KRAS G12C mutation?<br />\n<br />\n有嘅話ARS-1620呢隻標靶藥應該work架喎...<br />\n<br />\n利申:喺美帝頭五大醫學院入面研究cancer, 包括colon cancer."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:35:32.000Z","msg":"之前有驗血有驗過KRAS, 醫生話反應係Negative，所以無用相關嘅藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nKRAS隻藥就係免疫治療嘅藥?"},{"pid":"1c9ef6d333e3f8b67ceb3fd96b1d343bff701aa6","tid":862322,"uid":84734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"974ee97b744eab3b3f3a996b712a5efd15c133c7","tid":862322,"uid":43000,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:34:04.000Z","msg":"佐敦協成行7樓 施醫生有做，一針4萬幾蚊(唔同劑量唔同價錢)<br />\n我屋企人前排有cancer做左半年，好好彩癌細胞指數落返正常水平<br />\n不過唔係個個啱用同埋每次做完記得睇返癌細胞指數有無好轉，因為聽講有啲醫生好hea收完錢就算完全唔理有無成效<br />\n希望你屋企人無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:37:12.000Z","msg":"巴打你屋企人係咪都係大腸癌?<br />\n同埋個醫生有無講係邊隻藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd6730e69b4cd4b29651722f6c63be9b108a0f8c","tid":862322,"uid":43000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c9ef6d333e3f8b67ceb3fd96b1d343bff701aa6","tid":862322,"uid":84734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"974ee97b744eab3b3f3a996b712a5efd15c133c7","tid":862322,"uid":43000,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:34:04.000Z","msg":"佐敦協成行7樓 施醫生有做，一針4萬幾蚊(唔同劑量唔同價錢)<br />\n我屋企人前排有cancer做左半年，好好彩癌細胞指數落返正常水平<br />\n不過唔係個個啱用同埋每次做完記得睇返癌細胞指數有無好轉，因為聽講有啲醫生好hea收完錢就算完全唔理有無成效<br />\n希望你屋企人無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:37:12.000Z","msg":"巴打你屋企人係咪都係大腸癌?<br />\n同埋個醫生有無講係邊隻藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:45:17.000Z","msg":"肺癌<br />\n唔係我陪佢去睇所以唔知藥名"},{"pid":"29e8d8cfdd0df73810702cbb1182d90a2c27c7cb","tid":862322,"uid":84734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd6730e69b4cd4b29651722f6c63be9b108a0f8c","tid":862322,"uid":43000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c9ef6d333e3f8b67ceb3fd96b1d343bff701aa6","tid":862322,"uid":84734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"974ee97b744eab3b3f3a996b712a5efd15c133c7","tid":862322,"uid":43000,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:34:04.000Z","msg":"佐敦協成行7樓 施醫生有做，一針4萬幾蚊(唔同劑量唔同價錢)<br />\n我屋企人前排有cancer做左半年，好好彩癌細胞指數落返正常水平<br />\n不過唔係個個啱用同埋每次做完記得睇返癌細胞指數有無好轉，因為聽講有啲醫生好hea收完錢就算完全唔理有無成效<br />\n希望你屋企人無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:37:12.000Z","msg":"巴打你屋企人係咪都係大腸癌?<br />\n同埋個醫生有無講係邊隻藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:45:17.000Z","msg":"肺癌<br />\n唔係我陪佢去睇所以唔知藥名"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:51:38.000Z","msg":"好多謝巴打你咁夜仲覆我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我爸爸做化療果時都有每兩星期驗一次血，但d指數就升下跌下，個醫生直情話個指數唔準<br />\n但去照超聲波就照到個肝有好多一點點<br />\n但佢而家轉左中醫之後就無再驗血同照超聲波，中醫師話驚佢無事都嚇到有事，而且之前每一次等報告都真係對佢好大壓力"},{"pid":"9b6ff3cadfd3724461e7f34319a91f2b6f263975","tid":862322,"uid":67171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:51:48.000Z","msg":"你爸爸睇邊個中醫？"},{"pid":"df324404c8b06314e6436757a327ff9721e3afd3","tid":862322,"uid":84734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b6ff3cadfd3724461e7f34319a91f2b6f263975","tid":862322,"uid":67171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:51:48.000Z","msg":"你爸爸睇邊個中醫？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:59:03.000Z","msg":"凌遠志中醫<br />\n一開始我都唔想佢信哂中醫，但自從睇左個中醫之後，真係睇得出個人精神左好多，最緊要係磅數加返，血氣好左<br />\n但係而家冇驗任何野同埋出事嘅係肝，好擔心會有一日突然就出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed8ebb10d12b6a9d1f38860fb36bdb22210e099d","tid":862322,"uid":75232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3298ad8e882ebfae93279dca78b6e241f4827559","tid":862322,"uid":84734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73cc445a019d2eb1333194db646eb0b5ce8b95ee","tid":862322,"uid":75232,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:15:16.000Z","msg":"你Daddy個colon cancer有無KRAS G12C mutation?<br />\n<br />\n有嘅話ARS-1620呢隻標靶藥應該work架喎...<br />\n<br />\n利申:喺美帝頭五大醫學院入面研究cancer, 包括colon cancer."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:35:32.000Z","msg":"之前有驗血有驗過KRAS, 醫生話反應係Negative，所以無用相關嘅藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nKRAS隻藥就係免疫治療嘅藥?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T19:16:16.000Z","msg":"KRAS呢隻係標靶化療藥唔係免疫療法。"},{"pid":"47e40510b1ef977f77d0aecc5ea1e602141ac651","tid":862322,"uid":84734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T03:10:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"069c5ac072eb7a86ed3773946db709b5760dbbcc","tid":862322,"uid":60628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T06:52:04.000Z","msg":"免疫療法響大腸癌唔算特別發達<br />\n因為好多現存藥都好有效"},{"pid":"6be0a8b403e84424a1832f6a5c4a85f9966f9886","tid":862322,"uid":86686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df324404c8b06314e6436757a327ff9721e3afd3","tid":862322,"uid":84734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b6ff3cadfd3724461e7f34319a91f2b6f263975","tid":862322,"uid":67171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:51:48.000Z","msg":"你爸爸睇邊個中醫？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:59:03.000Z","msg":"凌遠志中醫<br />\n一開始我都唔想佢信哂中醫，但自從睇左個中醫之後，真係睇得出個人精神左好多，最緊要係磅數加返，血氣好左<br />\n但係而家冇驗任何野同埋出事嘅係肝，好擔心會有一日突然就出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T02:39:50.000Z","msg":"我想問, 你爸睇中醫前有咩病癥? <br />\n<br />\n我都有家人患末期cancer, 化療左成年, 而家想睇中醫<br />\n但15 16未揀定邊個好<br />\n而家想盡快make decision睇邊個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ff83dd369f6ea6b6822f9f04c481d645951f54","tid":862322,"uid":210755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T02:42:50.000Z","msg":"過程中，研究人員先將病人體內會攻擊癌細胞的T細胞抽出， 然後在實驗室大量培植，再將約900億個T細胞輸入患者體內"},{"pid":"50d0adf4ed56d6563347fba65e29e159c3e60dbd","tid":862322,"uid":210755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64ff83dd369f6ea6b6822f9f04c481d645951f54","tid":862322,"uid":210755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T02:42:50.000Z","msg":"過程中，研究人員先將病人體內會攻擊癌細胞的T細胞抽出， 然後在實驗室大量培植，再將約900億個T細胞輸入患者體內"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T02:43:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.omgtw.com/article/56965\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.omgtw.com%2Farticle%2F56965&d=jebdwlTiQyTJVUSyhQpfiYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=fd5f03eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.omgtw.com/article/56965</a>"},{"pid":"0393809a8959a294a9662522413cd98ed3965f00","tid":862322,"uid":84734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6be0a8b403e84424a1832f6a5c4a85f9966f9886","tid":862322,"uid":86686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df324404c8b06314e6436757a327ff9721e3afd3","tid":862322,"uid":84734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b6ff3cadfd3724461e7f34319a91f2b6f263975","tid":862322,"uid":67171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:51:48.000Z","msg":"你爸爸睇邊個中醫？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:59:03.000Z","msg":"凌遠志中醫<br />\n一開始我都唔想佢信哂中醫，但自從睇左個中醫之後，真係睇得出個人精神左好多，最緊要係磅數加返，血氣好左<br />\n但係而家冇驗任何野同埋出事嘅係肝，好擔心會有一日突然就出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T02:39:50.000Z","msg":"我想問, 你爸睇中醫前有咩病癥? <br />\n<br />\n我都有家人患末期cancer, 化療左成年, 而家想睇中醫<br />\n但15 16未揀定邊個好<br />\n而家想盡快make decision睇邊個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T03:03:33.000Z","msg":"佢d病徵全部都係化療d副作用黎，手指麻痹，皮膚變差，甩頭髮，無胃口，肚瀉，愈黎愈瘦等等，真係由個cancer 引發嘅病徵就無見過<br />\n<br />\n化療斷斷續續做左2年，但係照超聲波都一路照到d腫瘤愈生愈大粒，同埋化療d副作用太辛苦，所以決定轉中醫<br />\n<br />\n而家轉左中醫同做返運動，之前化療嘅副作用都無哂，最緊要而家肥返d，心情又好左<br />\n<br />\n做決定真係好痛苦，巴打唔好放棄，唔好俾你屋企人覺得到左末期就玩完"},{"pid":"97d8645a1eae0bdee72d9b742b2d3bc84feb8215","tid":862322,"uid":194415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T04:08:25.000Z","msg":"連登仔話中醫廢，呃人<br />\n叫你地唔好比中醫呃<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw<br />\n中醫係冇辦法醫 4 期<br />\n止到痛，食到訓到已經唔錯<br />\n夠舒服地拖住條命，活得一日得一日<br />\n呢個階段好過西醫<br />\n<br />\n氣功係 4 期亦冇助（一個氣功師重要用唔會多返嘅氣黎救4 期，機會不大，除非你好有錢）無謂錢"},{"pid":"e5178972ec4027fb08b254bde462cd33dcc5bb11","tid":862322,"uid":86686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0393809a8959a294a9662522413cd98ed3965f00","tid":862322,"uid":84734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6be0a8b403e84424a1832f6a5c4a85f9966f9886","tid":862322,"uid":86686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df324404c8b06314e6436757a327ff9721e3afd3","tid":862322,"uid":84734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T18:59:03.000Z","msg":"凌遠志中醫<br />\n一